My initial thought is =E2=80=93 this is 50,000 feet =E2=80=93 we need to =
be at 1,000 feet =E2=80=93 but then that is what makes us good business =
partners! My concern is that the 50,000 feet words makes us look cool =
but doesn=E2=80=99t get us customers. I=E2=80=99ll counter with:

=20

You are living in a tight labour market where talent is scarce.

=20

You are living in an age where everyone has their values and DE&I policy =
on the wall but frustration is building around lack of day to day =
action.

=20

You need data that allows you to give everyone in your organisation and =
opportunity to develop the critical skills they will need for the future =
=E2=80=93 their soft skills.

=20

You need data that allows you to consistently identify individuals that =
are living your values day to day =E2=80=93 and put actions in place to =
retain those people.

=20

You need a platform that links the words on the wall to day to day =
actions.

=20

Indigometrics is that platform. The future is values led. Will you be a =
part of it?

=20

C

=20

