=20

10,000 feet here, but I want to distill the vision of the future that =
Indigo plays a part of. Thoughts?

=20

- J

=20

=20

#######

=20

The future of work is distributed, autonomous, and permeable - many =
discrete parts loosely joined and dynamically coupling as quickly =
changing market conditions demand.

=20

It is also a global future, where pricing will be set more by universal =
rates and availability than disparate local conditions. This males price =
a minor point of leverage.

=20

In this future, values allow organizations to coordinate flexibly across =
swiftly moving targets by retreating even further from micromanagement. =
At the same time, values provide an inviolable hedge against competition =
for talent as well as producing significant new consumer appeal.

=20

What is required for success in this future is a set of value metrics =
which translate directly to key operational behaviors and deliverables. =
A =E2=80=9CP&L of culture=E2=80=9D that allows leaders to manage their =
entire organization by driving values and managing returns (evolving =
KPIs) instead of endlessly implementing slow-moving burocratic =
processes.

=20

Indigometrics is that tool. The future is values led. Will you be a part =
of it?

=20

- J

=20


